   {
      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "@Fi3 found the issue, fixed in a7f08e74428c4e5da62365d686e5c51c5afc959d\r\n\r\n```patch\r\n--- a/src/common/sv2_noise.cpp\r\n+++ b/src/common/sv2_noise.cpp\r\n@@ -56,11 +56,11 @@ void Sv2CipherState::EncryptMessage(Span<std::byte> input, Span<std::byte> outpu\r\n     for (size_t i = 0; i < num_chunks; ++i) {\r\n         size_t chunk_start = i * max_chunk_size;\r\n         size_t chunk_end = std::min(chunk_start + max_chunk_size, input.size());\r\n         size_t chunk_size = chunk_end - chunk_start;\r\n         const auto encrypted_chunk_start = output.begin() + i * NOISE_MAX_CHUNK_SIZE;\r\n-        std::copy(input.begin(), input.begin() + chunk_size, encrypted_chunk_start);\r\n+        std::copy(input.begin() + chunk_start, input.begin() + chunk_start + chunk_size, encrypted_chunk_start);\r\n```",
